ts do not occur, and thus large $Q$-values can be obtained when\nthey are operated below $\\gamma_r$. We find that $K_r$ for amorphous resonators\nis comparable to that for resonators with crystalline order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Jun 2019 19:43:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
