 approaches. The personalization factor for assessing\nthe stimulus (surprise) strength further helps the recommender achieve smaller\n(better) inter-user similarity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Jun 2019 00:08:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Feb 2020 18:05:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-18"}
