ly missing in {\\omega}\nCen. The discrepancy between our field hot subdwarf stars and the EHB stas in\n{\\omega} Cen indicate different origins for the two counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Jun 2019 01:37:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
